      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TODD KEEPING (2) was game in defeat at the latest run, finishing third and beaten 1.75 lengths (19.65) behind Stifler at Murray Bridge. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Racing well and deserves a win. IMAGINE THE FUN (1) has a strong record this trip with 10 wins and five placings from 22 starts. In the money last time at this track (22.54) in a Free For All, finishing a nose second. Makes strong appeal on best. CARRY ON CASEY (8) has a strong overall record having 11 wins and 17 places from 38 starts but was out of the money last time when fourth (19.26) over 350m at Murray Bridge. Form at the trip sound including four wins. Looks well placed here and has the ability. Go well. RED SAID SO (6) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.",
